Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,how wonderful to be here. Our lecture today is basically about peace, and our main question that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we ask ourselves is, is peace external or is peace internal? So I'm going to ask David to say just a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,couple words on that right now. Is peace external or is it internal? Peace is an internal affair,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah. Sometimes it leaks out into the world. Peace is an internal affair, yes. If they don't
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,turn off that music now, I'm going to kill them. I want peace, and I want it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:02:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good way to start the lecture. On the way here today, the awareness came to mind that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,mind thinks, but spirit knows. Oh, that's good. The mind thinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,mind thinks, yeah, thinks about things, you know, and the mind is really an instrument of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,endlessly discuss things, argue, and spirit just knows silently. Spirit did that. Now mind will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,talk about it, but it was spirit that grabs my sweetheart's arm. Spirit is an instrument of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so God just grabbed your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in touch with your God nature. Your spirit is your godly nature, and the mind is the ego's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,nature. The human life is, of course, the mind spinning around, but it's really the spirit that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,accounts for your existence. The mind would like to convince you that your survival is up to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind says, if you don't listen to me, you won't make it to the end, etc. Yeah, but spirit is the one,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that knows, mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the time, can you tell them about the truck, when you were down in Patagonia, and,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and, you know, you'd broken down, and the truck was smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them that story, because that was more of the spirit than it was your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that wasn't mind at all, no. Sometimes spirit, well, no, I didn't hear thoughts, I just knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in Patagonia, which is down near the southern border, in my old truck, 68, or 64,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it is, big willis truck, and, uh, I was many miles, 150 miles, probably from the nearest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,civilization, and I had parked the truck and, uh, when I came back to start the truck, I turned the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,key and smoke shot out from under the hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God the engine is on fire and here I am a million miles from nowhere and I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,already had heat exhaustion I did I had very little energy to begin with and so
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:05:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,here the engine is on fire and I and I'd run out of water and I wasn't exactly an
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced desert hiker you know run out of water so anyway the smoke is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,pouring out from under the hood even if you open the hood you wouldn't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to see where it was coming from and I thought well I guess you're gonna die
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,here now so I sat back I thought well it's time to leave I'll leave every time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been close to death I sit around waiting for it to happen in the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,miraculous hours occurs so anyway I was all set to leave the planet all of a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,sudden an interruption occurred and I was in the middle of the night and I was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the night as well and I was in the middle of the night and I was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the night and I was going to sleep there and in the next
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,minute of the night as I was about to go to bed my inner voice said to me well I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,had a plastic cup with about this much coffee still in the bottom maybe half
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,inch of coffee so an inner knowingness the inner knowingness was take this cup
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,plastic polyester cup and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it through the bottom of the glove compartment. Well, the bottom of the glove compartment in your
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,car, you think it's made of something solid, but it isn't. It's just heavy-duty cardboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I rammed it through this cardboard, and I took this cup, and I put it in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I heard a sizzle, and the fire went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's one reason I'm still here. But anyway, a knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a non-verbal knowingness, is the voice of spirit. That's the voice of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And people complain they've never spoken to God, and God's been talking to them for 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and they don't even realize what it is. I always thought it was Susie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's God talking through her, so I listen carefully when she speaks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Respectfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to go ahead and start this. I think we've got everyone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the lecture today is on peace. We want to welcome all of you. I know a lot of you have
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,come here from Canada, different areas, and we want to thank you for making that trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And at this time, I'd like to introduce Dr. David R. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria and Excelsius Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to thee, O Lord, Most High. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are we talking about today? I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, peace. Right, yes. I knew we were talking about something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have some slides on the subject of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a pen. That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar. I've told that story before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was way up in the Andes, up near Machu Picchu, and there wasn't anybody for miles and miles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,around, and maybe, I forget how many thousand feet it was, over 10,000 feet. And I go through
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,this narrow passageway, and here's a young girl standing there, and she's got a llama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, can I take your picture with that llama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, that'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how I got into saying, that'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, where is the first slides?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we use this thing as a pointer, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good for small children and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how many people are here for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless all the people who are here for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about being here for the first time is you can only be here for the first time once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is indeed a memorable occasion in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak from humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I've got more humility than anybody I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you have to be able to read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the right height for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it supposed to come down a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely well known and really known pretty much around the world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the historic levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The ancient knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's calibrated from one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:12:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And over on the left-hand side, you see the view of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the view of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of enlightenment, which calibrates from 700 to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And the emotion that goes with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the process that's going on in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is extremely comprehensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It includes just about everything that's possible to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, they had something on Fox News about a famous murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A famous murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Up right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where he calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know where it calibrates without even using the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The most serial killers and all calibrate around 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,30.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything below 200 is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we use the arm to find out whether a thing is true or false...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200 is falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And 200 and up is truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use it on politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,200 and up is truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the quick way to find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the presence of truth, the body goes strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the presence of falsehood, it goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an idiot can get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a protoplasmic, in my understanding, protoplasmic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That for life to survive, it had to be able to discern poison from food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the little bacteria or little organisms had to have some way of knowing this stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,here will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff here will make you grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those that didn't learn it are no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a basic knowingness of life forms starting out at the lowest forms of protoplasm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and going on up to the highest level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But with it, you're capable of knowing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the thing that's the most mind-boggling of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The most mind-boggling thing of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you won't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is within an instant, you can tell the truth about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything with a capital A.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything now or ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that ever occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can know the truth about anything in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes one instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This crowd here calibrates over 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,400.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,420.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,440.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,435.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,430.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This group here calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This group here calibrates over 430.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do the United...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The United States Congress calibrates over 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,350.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You calibrate higher than the United States Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good enough for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it's a spiritually oriented group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To be spiritually oriented tends to lift your level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and throw you in the company of others that are like-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are spiritually oriented tend to gravitate towards each other
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and are attracted to each other and feel comfortable and at home with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is very famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's these levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called the map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's printed in all the languages in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,29 languages or 30 languages or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's commonly known now throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, due to our own work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, due to its practicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to read a whole book to get that a thing could...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,By using the arm, you can calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either truthful or it's not truthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it is truthful, what level of truth is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is extremely useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, today what we're talking about is peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,which as a state of consciousness calibrates at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace as a way of being in the world is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Political peace is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:18:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But peace as a level of consciousness is an extremely high state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you have to give up the attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to all the other things that would pull you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see, shame and guilt, apathy, grief, fear, cravingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,anger, pridefulness are all in the lower levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage is at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody's going to help me out, if I'm in the armed forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,who do I want to come and get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm laying there, just been shot, about to get blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want somebody right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want somebody in pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want somebody who's going to talk to me and reason about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:19:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If they love me, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just flowery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want somebody with courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage. I want somebody with courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who says, you're about to get blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always give this thing, when I was in the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and this mine is right next to the minesweeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We were sweeping the East China Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's this mine, came up from the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it's got these things sticking out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Horns, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, the horn is almost touching the side of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to get blown to bits any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're holding this thing away with boat poles to keep it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So this other guy is helping me, and he looks at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, what if it blows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, well, then we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told him the truth, and the sincerity of it was just what he needed to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I was so bland about dying is I'd had near-death experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and been out of body and all that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, there really wasn't anything to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave the body, and those of you who have had the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look at the body, it's laying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nowhere, particularly in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the body's laying there, and it doesn't really look all that interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You wonder why you were ever so attached to it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so these are the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're going to be talking about peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which is actually the highest level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, to reach the state of peace, you've got to let go of shaming yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to get rid of attacking yourself with guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to care enough about life that you're no longer in apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to get over feeling grief about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you're screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask if you were scared, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you to climb up that mast and fix that goddamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up in the mast, and I have a fear of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And they said, don't look down, Shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a stupid idiot, from the top of the mast, I looked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The body just, the body went into involuntary spasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The bosun's mate said, I'm going to have to come up and get you, Shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let go of the mast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He came up in the bosun's chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the boxing champion of the third fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said, Shorty, I'm going to have to cold cock you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not let go of the mast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The bodies were in involuntary spasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the champion of the third fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.66,0:22:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a ferocious boxer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And he had an incredible knockout punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just, I said, okay, okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited for the knockout punch, and all of a sudden, the body let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Involuntary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like knowing where to pour that cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The involuntariness of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutral is, it's okay if it goes this way, and it's okay if it goes that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness at 310.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance at 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:23:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The high 300s are very, very powerful in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a worldly person, these are the levels you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The great multimillionaires.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the one that keeps buying casinos and buying whole countries?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, they all calibrate in high 300s.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is sort of a way of being in the world where acquisition and mastery is motivating just for its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To own more gambling casinos than any other person in the world is just the gratification of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Got enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But just to be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you get to the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you talk about the intellect and reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything of great note is in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.70,0:24:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy is 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace is 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are all energizing as you go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Energizing and energizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But peace is no longer energizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go into a state of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sit on a rock all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.83,0:24:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And people have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to go in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.42,0:24:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to get sun stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.42,0:24:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You say okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.42,0:24:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So peace is a divine state.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.74,0:24:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of the divine states.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.74,0:24:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.74,0:24:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.74,0:24:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough of the calibrated levels?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.96,0:24:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the Enlightenment 600 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.64,0:24:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme Godhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.64,0:24:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,God Manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.64,0:24:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.64,0:24:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Archangels.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.75,0:24:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.75,0:24:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddhahood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.75,0:24:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.75,0:24:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brahman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.75,0:24:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.75,0:24:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are called avatars.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.07,0:24:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.07,0:25:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.07,0:25:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.07,0:25:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.27,0:25:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the energy field in microwatts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.27,0:25:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In microwatts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.27,0:25:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the energy field of the calibrated levels translates into the physics of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.27,0:25:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see that the amount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.27,0:25:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see down here these people don't have much energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.27,0:25:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.27,0:25:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And they don't care enough about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.27,0:25:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it takes more energy for brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.27,0:25:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,500 is the level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.27,0:25:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,600 is selfless love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.27,0:25:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are the levels of enlightenment which go up to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.27,0:25:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.26,0:25:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the world's population.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.26,0:25:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason peace is so rare in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.26,0:25:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,People think peace is whatever that you call that when there's no war.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.26,0:25:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.39,0:25:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the world's population calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.51,0:26:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,200 is the level of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.51,0:26:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.51,0:26:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of truth is 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.51,0:26:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the world's population calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.70,0:26:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.70,0:26:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains the nature of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.70,0:26:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point in trying to make it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.70,0:26:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that people have not reached the point of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.70,0:26:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,People keep going back to jail for minor crimes over and over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.70,0:26:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, well, after three or four trips they've been arrested for stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.70,0:26:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they go and do it all over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.70,0:26:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they're down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.04,0:26:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.04,0:26:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.04,0:26:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.04,0:26:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the world's population.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.11,0:26:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the world's population.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.66,0:26:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, only 15% of the world's population is above 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.77,0:26:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The implication of this is staggering.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.77,0:26:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.77,0:27:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.92,0:27:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 15% of human population calibrates above the level of integrity, 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.21,0:27:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.29,0:27:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means the average person will steal you blind if you give him a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.83,0:27:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As we know from the Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.83,0:27:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,15% of the people are above 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.27,0:27:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So why doesn't mankind then just fall off into the ocean and drown?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.84,0:27:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's because the 15% have so much power that they totally counterbalance all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.84,0:27:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,85% would not even be able to survive on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.84,0:28:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This 15% is what keeps mankind alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.03,0:28:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.03,0:28:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.72,0:28:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The evolution of consciousness over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.94,0:28:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is percent of elapsed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.86,0:28:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see consciousness stayed way down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.86,0:28:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then only in the last few minutes of human history did it rise up to the current level.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.86,0:28:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.86,0:28:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The current level of consciousness of mankind overall is, let's see, it's over 202, 205, 208, 206, 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.64,0:28:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Overall mankind calibrates 206.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.00,0:28:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.00,0:28:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.00,0:28:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the great evolutionary early epics and their calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.00,0:28:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, life begins as protozoa and bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.00,0:28:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at one or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.00,0:29:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you see the marine, the fish, then the animals, the reptiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.50,0:29:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we move up the scale of the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.01,0:29:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.01,0:29:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And we get to the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.00,0:29:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now here's one we're very familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.07,0:29:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have bacteria, insects, fish, Komodo dragon, reptiles, snakes, alligators.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.58,0:29:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the dinosaurs, whale, dolphin, migratory birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.80,0:29:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.80,0:29:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's just fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.80,0:29:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the animal kingdom, and it's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.94,0:29:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A dove calibrates at 145.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.94,0:29:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A grizzly bear at 160.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.94,0:29:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fool around with grizzly bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.76,0:29:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At 160, they have only one interest, and that's to find out if you're good eating or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.76,0:30:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to the hippopotamus.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.22,0:30:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to the deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.22,0:30:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, below level 200, that's the great demarcation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.47,0:30:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Below level 200, animal life is predatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.81,0:30:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They live by the death of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.81,0:30:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,From 200 and up arise the herbivores.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.81,0:30:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The herbivores survive without killing anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.81,0:30:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.81,0:30:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cow doesn't have to kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.81,0:30:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to kill anybody to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.07,0:30:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So here, now you get to the deer and the piggy and the oak, the dairy cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.20,0:30:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're moving up the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.42,0:30:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The farm horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.42,0:30:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cats are at 240.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.42,0:30:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The family cat is at 245.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.76,0:30:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs are at 240.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.76,0:30:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The family dog is at 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.76,0:30:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we go on up to gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.76,0:30:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.76,0:31:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex the trained gray parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.93,0:31:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco the trained gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.93,0:31:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the Coco the trained gorilla
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.93,0:31:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates higher than 95% of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.58,0:31:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember when that baby was dropped in the gorilla pit
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the gorilla went over and picked up the baby
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.06,0:31:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and set it over where the keeper could come in the gate and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.06,0:31:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't do that in other parts of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.07,0:31:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They just kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.65,0:31:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so Oscar the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.09,0:31:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar's the cat that knows when you're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.09,0:31:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a famous cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.42,0:31:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who Oscar the cat is?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.42,0:31:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If Oscar goes and sleeps with you, you're due to die within 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.71,0:31:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in a nursing home, and they found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.41,0:31:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar knew when somebody was going to leave the world within 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.41,0:32:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would go and sleep with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.41,0:32:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And sure enough, within 24 hours, they were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.41,0:32:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so here's the Songbirds song.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.79,0:32:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, here's the cat's purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.79,0:32:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat's purr is at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.79,0:32:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And a dog's wagging tail is at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.79,0:32:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So when the cat is sleeping next to you in the bed going,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.11,0:32:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,purr, purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.11,0:32:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it's like music.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.11,0:32:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.11,0:32:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The next happy thing is you get up in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.33,0:32:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because the cat got you purring,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.33,0:32:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's the doggie, and the doggie's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.33,0:32:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dog's wagging tail is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.39,0:32:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional low.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.02,0:32:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional low.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.11,0:32:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always interested in advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.11,0:32:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And those ads that show a dog with a wagging tail
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.11,0:32:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate much higher than all the other ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.11,0:32:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to sell more bush beans,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.21,0:33:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a dog with a wagging tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.17,0:33:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Purr, purr, purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.26,0:33:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a cat. I had to teach him how to purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.26,0:33:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't know how to purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.48,0:33:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my $50 cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.48,0:33:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd spend $50 for a cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.48,0:33:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but this cat was unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.64,0:33:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And we brought him home, and he didn't know how to purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.64,0:33:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited for him to purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.64,0:33:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had a cat that didn't purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.64,0:33:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't know how to purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.85,0:33:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to show him how to purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.85,0:33:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I took him to bed, and I'm purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.85,0:33:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I held him next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.85,0:33:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so he could feel the vibration in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.85,0:33:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Purr, purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.40,0:33:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know, he's going purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.40,0:33:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.38,0:33:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to teach him he could do it on the exhale,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.38,0:33:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had to teach him how to do it on the inhale.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.73,0:33:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I go purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.73,0:34:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing I know, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.59,0:34:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So people who don't like cats or dogs, beware of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.71,0:34:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who doesn't like a dog's wagging tail
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.71,0:34:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or a kitty's fur better carry a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.00,0:34:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move next.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.38,0:34:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Books of the Western World.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.38,0:34:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is of profound importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.38,0:34:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Renaissance,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.38,0:34:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the Great Books of the Western World.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.38,0:34:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And here you see all the great minds of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.38,0:34:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles Darwin, Dostoevsky,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.44,0:34:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great names.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.44,0:34:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hippocrates, Hegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.78,0:34:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see all the great names.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.78,0:34:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakespeare, Adam Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.11,0:34:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are all the great names of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.11,0:35:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go to college, this is what you don't know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.11,0:35:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but when you go to college,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.11,0:35:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what you're supposed to be learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.67,0:35:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to become acquainted with the great minds of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go to college to learn the great minds of history,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.19,0:35:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you do, except that now the far left has taken over,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.19,0:35:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see what's wrong with the far left
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.19,0:35:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is that Karl Marx calibrates at 130.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.01,0:35:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Karl Marx so low?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.67,0:35:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does not teach the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.67,0:35:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.67,0:35:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Marxism is at 130.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.67,0:35:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason the far left calibrates low
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.67,0:35:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is because it's based on the proposition of perpetrator and victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.71,0:35:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dualistic perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.84,0:35:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And this dualistic perception projects onto the world
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.84,0:35:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,victim and perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.84,0:35:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're poor, it's got to be somebody's fault
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.84,0:35:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that they caused you to be poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.84,0:35:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that you're lazy, didn't pay any attention in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.94,0:36:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and are drunk all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.94,0:36:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.48,0:36:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The haves are responsible for creating the have-nots, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.88,0:36:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's tried as a social system.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.88,0:36:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't worked out anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.88,0:36:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We have lots of politicians that keep trying to put it onto us
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.53,0:36:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it hasn't worked anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.53,0:36:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me someplace where it's worked in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.53,0:36:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll gain some enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.53,0:36:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.55,0:36:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.61,0:36:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to do with a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.61,0:36:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.84,0:36:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the event, however, only takes place
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.84,0:36:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,within a certain field of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So an event is defined actually by the field
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.84,0:36:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in which it seems to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.84,0:36:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.88,0:37:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.88,0:37:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have put this one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.88,0:37:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too good a one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.76,0:37:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have the difference between lower mind and higher mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.03,0:37:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as we evolve from the animal kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.03,0:37:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you now come to the lower mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.03,0:37:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the lower mind wants things.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.03,0:37:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.03,0:37:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's callous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.03,0:37:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the people who go to jail all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.03,0:37:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time beating up people,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.03,0:37:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,their indifference to the suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.03,0:37:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the suffering of others, totally insensitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.03,0:37:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,completely selfish, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.03,0:37:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And they depend on force.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.32,0:37:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And higher mind is more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.34,0:37:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher mind, which is more typical of this audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.34,0:37:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, is more sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.34,0:37:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It tends to be merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.34,0:37:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It tends to serve all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.34,0:37:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.34,0:38:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.67,0:38:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.67,0:38:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This side actually has power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.67,0:38:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And this side here depends on force.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.67,0:38:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This depends on force.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.67,0:38:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I want somebody to follow me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.61,0:38:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't use something to beat them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.61,0:38:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to persuade them that this is the best way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.61,0:38:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.94,0:38:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We persuade people.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.28,0:38:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.34,0:38:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in which form begins to register within mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.34,0:38:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing it runs into
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.63,0:38:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which watches and experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.63,0:38:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an aspect of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.63,0:38:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the observer, the witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.63,0:38:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,which doesn't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.63,0:38:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of consciousness arises out of the Godhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.82,0:39:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of God as creator arises the light of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.67,0:39:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we do is consciousness research.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.15,0:39:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're really doing is constantly researching
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.19,0:39:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what could otherwise be called the mind of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.19,0:39:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which is consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.19,0:39:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.26,0:39:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and has no beginning and has no end
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.36,0:39:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and has no limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.36,0:39:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and is infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.44,0:39:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With spiritual evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.34,0:39:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.34,0:39:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and you reach an inner state of quietude.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.34,0:39:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that's easiest and most obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.34,0:39:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to get to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.34,0:39:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is the observer, the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.38,0:39:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You observe and witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.38,0:39:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't think anything about it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.38,0:39:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or say anything about it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.38,0:39:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or argue anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.63,0:39:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I observe someone sitting at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.63,0:39:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.63,0:40:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.71,0:40:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.71,0:40:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't need...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.80,0:40:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The observer witness doesn't think about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.03,0:40:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So move on to the next then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.03,0:40:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to become acquainted
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.21,0:40:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because you have to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.21,0:40:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how you're going to have peace in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.21,0:40:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,without understanding the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.36,0:40:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The human brain, left and right brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.71,0:40:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as your animal brain then,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.71,0:40:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your animal brain below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.84,0:40:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it sees something happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.17,0:40:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly it goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.42,0:40:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It bypasses the cortex
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.42,0:40:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and goes directly to the emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.78,0:40:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,goes to the emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.78,0:40:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.36,0:40:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the emotional side of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.48,0:40:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really the animal side.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.90,0:41:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.15,0:41:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you're run by the animal brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.15,0:41:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which is into fight or flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.15,0:41:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The alarm reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.23,0:41:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,disrupts the acupuncture meridians.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.84,0:41:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative muscle test response.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.88,0:41:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.67,0:41:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The other side of the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.67,0:41:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is the spiritual side.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.67,0:41:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The right brain dominance
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.67,0:41:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.73,0:41:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the source of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.73,0:41:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're talking about peace today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.73,0:41:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.73,0:41:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is the release of endorphins
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.73,0:41:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,within your brain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.84,0:41:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,associated with positive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.84,0:41:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The peaceful endorphins,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.94,0:41:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual side of your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.03,0:41:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,brings about healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.03,0:41:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,balances your acupuncture system,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.03,0:41:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get a positive muscle test response.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.26,0:42:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're talking about today then
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.26,0:42:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is serenity,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.55,0:42:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,peacefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.55,0:42:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way of being in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.55,0:42:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,because that activates the kundalini energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.55,0:42:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.55,0:42:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to rise up into the right side of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.55,0:42:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And that alters all your responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.71,0:42:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So a fearful person
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.71,0:42:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,looks over there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.71,0:42:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and is frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.80,0:42:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And a person who's more into endorphins
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.80,0:42:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,looks over there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.80,0:42:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and is interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.84,0:42:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So the endorphins support life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.44,0:42:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.38,0:42:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.38,0:42:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and social problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.38,0:42:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.15,0:42:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,here's the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.38,0:42:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.38,0:42:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,People or a community
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.38,0:42:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or a country
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.38,0:43:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or a neighborhood, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.36,0:43:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the rate of unemployment?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.36,0:43:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing as unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.36,0:43:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is very much in the news today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.36,0:43:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.03,0:43:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.55,0:43:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.55,0:43:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of unemployment,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.55,0:43:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,as you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.55,0:43:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,increases
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.55,0:43:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the lower the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.78,0:43:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.78,0:43:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,does not decrease
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.78,0:43:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in direct line
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.63,0:43:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with the number of jobs available
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.15,0:43:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,as everyone presumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.15,0:43:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.32,0:43:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason they're unemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.32,0:43:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is because there aren't any jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.32,0:43:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.92,0:43:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the power is given to,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.01,0:43:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is given outside the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.01,0:43:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm unemployed,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.40,0:43:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there's only one reason
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.40,0:43:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.61,0:43:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one reason
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.73,0:43:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.73,0:43:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.48,0:44:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul cause of unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.94,0:44:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.94,0:44:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After World War II,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.19,0:44:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.38,0:44:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But whenever there were no jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.38,0:44:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I always had three or four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.57,0:44:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I drove cab at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.57,0:44:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I drove cab during the day
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.34,0:44:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or the bartender at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.73,0:44:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're broke
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.73,0:44:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and you haven't got any money,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.73,0:44:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the quickest thing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.73,0:44:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is you go down any street,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.73,0:44:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.73,0:44:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody can ever complain
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.73,0:44:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're unemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.73,0:44:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,after what I say next.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.73,0:44:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to run out,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.71,0:44:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,put your fingers in your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.71,0:44:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to listen to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.63,0:44:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't blame anybody anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.63,0:44:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.30,0:44:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.30,0:44:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You go down any street.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.23,0:44:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You knock on doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.51,0:44:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The lady opens the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.80,0:44:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.21,0:44:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you need any windows washed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.21,0:45:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never gone more than three houses
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.28,0:45:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without somebody employing me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.67,0:45:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,right on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.67,0:45:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dollar a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.67,0:45:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,20 minutes, I made $10.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.17,0:45:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go down to the next house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.51,0:45:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,By noon, I've made $95.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.19,0:45:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No income tax on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.19,0:45:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the next house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.19,0:45:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the next house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.96,0:45:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No income tax on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.78,0:45:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let anybody know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.84,0:45:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to be unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.84,0:45:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.92,0:45:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're disabled, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.92,0:45:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're disabled,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.92,0:45:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,like I am right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.92,0:45:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.92,0:45:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely walk around.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.15,0:45:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When you can't barely walk around,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.15,0:45:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.15,0:45:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You give lectures, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.53,0:46:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You write a book, sing a song,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.13,0:46:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,dance, be funny, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.09,0:46:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployment, then, is a lack of creativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.09,0:46:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a lack of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.32,0:46:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you ask God,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.32,0:46:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, I need a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.32,0:46:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please guide my steps in the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.48,0:46:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a job comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.73,0:46:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And failing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.73,0:46:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you knock on doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.34,0:46:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible to be unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.86,0:46:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the rate of unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.86,0:46:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,down below here is 97%.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.76,0:46:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always those people's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.76,0:46:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.76,0:46:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of unemployment here
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.13,0:46:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is based on blame and projecting,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.13,0:46:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,projecting their power into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.17,0:46:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has the power over your employment?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.51,0:46:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You or the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.51,0:46:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you reject it into the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.71,0:46:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,now you become a servant of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.71,0:47:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.69,0:47:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,amongst people of higher energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.69,0:47:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is practically zero percent
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.69,0:47:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,as you see it goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.69,0:47:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I certainly must have been
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.84,0:47:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in at least the 400s in those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.84,0:47:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And unemployment there was only 7%.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.94,0:47:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of poverty goes up in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.94,0:47:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.94,0:47:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the less the rate of poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.94,0:47:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.30,0:47:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Being broke is another.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.67,0:47:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been broke a lot of times in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.67,0:47:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't consider it poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.67,0:47:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I considered it being broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.51,0:47:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How is life?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.51,0:47:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy or not happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.51,0:47:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here, these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.51,0:47:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.51,0:47:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see slovenliness about life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.84,0:47:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.84,0:47:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your rate of happiness decreases
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.84,0:47:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to almost zero percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.84,0:47:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,These people think
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.84,0:48:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they're getting away with something,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.84,0:48:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.84,0:48:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all unhappy, all unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.84,0:48:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And as your consciousness level goes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.84,0:48:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of happiness becomes almost 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.84,0:48:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rate of criminality shows the reverse, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.86,0:48:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.86,0:48:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of criminality is rather rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.86,0:48:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And as your consciousness level goes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.86,0:48:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of criminality is close to 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.86,0:48:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.86,0:48:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Every bum knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.15,0:48:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to sleep on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.15,0:48:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you wake up, your shoes are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.15,0:48:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So always sleep on your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.53,0:48:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave them on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.57,0:48:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll take them off while you're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.63,0:48:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move next.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.88,0:48:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the susceptibility to AIDS
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.88,0:48:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,correlates with the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.88,0:49:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The lower the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.88,0:49:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the higher the rate of AIDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.88,0:49:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.51,0:49:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Levels of consciousness and rate of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.51,0:49:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We did that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.51,0:49:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that pridefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.67,0:49:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,cuts your rate of happiness to 22%.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.80,0:49:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And arrogance, anger, fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.80,0:49:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,all these things cut your rate of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.80,0:49:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage, then, from the level of truth on up,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.82,0:49:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the percent of happiness increases rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.82,0:49:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.88,0:49:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.46,0:49:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.59,0:49:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of great spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.59,0:49:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to know they're in several of the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.59,0:49:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All the great spiritual teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.78,0:49:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great spiritual teachers worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.78,0:49:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.78,0:49:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.53,0:49:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates was at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.88,0:50:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.44,0:50:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.50,0:50:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, I just wanted you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.50,0:50:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're all available and they're written in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.50,0:50:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to send us an email
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.50,0:50:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.59,0:50:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, we've got all these people listed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.59,0:50:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they always find somebody who's not on the list
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.59,0:50:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and send us an email about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.59,0:50:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.03,0:50:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.36,0:50:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.46,0:50:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is the difference between essence and perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.46,0:50:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference between essence and perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.48,0:50:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What a thing looks like is perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.48,0:50:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it consists of projections,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.67,0:50:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what you project onto a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.67,0:50:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Essence is what the thing really is within itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.67,0:50:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So here you see the wolf in sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.67,0:50:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf in sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.78,0:50:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside is the predator,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.07,0:51:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the predator who will steal from all the taxpayers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.07,0:51:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and buy themselves a couple of yachts and a private plane
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.07,0:51:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and villas around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.26,0:51:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.38,0:51:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we on this list?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.48,0:51:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.44,0:51:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, we're finally getting to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.44,0:51:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I just wanted to cover the basics
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.59,0:51:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for a common point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.59,0:51:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A point of reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.98,0:51:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.28,0:51:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not supposed to be at 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.28,0:51:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be at one, not 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.46,0:51:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from one to 101, you go from 101 backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.71,0:51:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.71,0:51:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.71,0:51:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shake it up, shake it up, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.30,0:51:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,101 ways to happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.84,0:51:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were talking about peace today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.84,0:51:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anybody being happy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.96,0:52:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up happiness, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.96,0:52:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.67,0:52:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.21,0:52:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.78,0:52:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the saddest story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.53,0:52:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everybody to make one, a little sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.53,0:52:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You put it on your mirror at home in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.96,0:52:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You stick it in the corner of the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.17,0:52:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.50,0:52:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.00,0:52:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it for seven days, you become a seven-day-er.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.98,0:52:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.63,0:53:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for six days, you cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.63,0:53:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.63,0:53:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You put a little sign there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.59,0:53:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, yours is the saddest story I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.59,0:53:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you put it in the corner of your mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.75,0:53:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will find that your life brightens up instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.88,0:53:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't cost you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.67,0:53:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even charge you a dollar for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.92,0:53:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.32,0:53:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it tilts your view of life into a different direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.32,0:53:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to see that, that kills self-pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.32,0:53:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It kills resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.32,0:53:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It kills blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.32,0:53:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It kills all the stuff that makes people miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.32,0:53:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it gets you back to the reality that the source of your own happiness is solely within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.32,0:53:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can take it away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.32,0:54:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I was telling all the headsmen, I said, listen, you got to do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.61,0:54:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.61,0:54:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.61,0:54:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.61,0:54:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop my head off if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.61,0:54:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.63,0:54:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his job to chop your head off, so why complain?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.71,0:54:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,101 ways to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.61,0:54:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one, you got to keep track of the time on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.94,0:54:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we getting to the break?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.63,0:54:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.63,0:54:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.34,0:54:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.34,0:54:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, we can cover the history of the world in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.94,0:54:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,101 ways to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.94,0:54:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, peacefulness then has to be a decision that you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.94,0:54:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Peacefulness can exist right in the middle of war and devastation and catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.30,0:55:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The ways to develop a peaceful nature, the first thing to do is to give up trying to change and control other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.25,0:55:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell them how to vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.07,0:55:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up questionable advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.30,0:55:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of trying to change and control others.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.30,0:55:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We always want other people to be different than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.23,0:55:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't they be more like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.40,0:55:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't change them, if I'm stuck with them, well, then at least I can control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.17,0:55:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.44,0:55:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll see how often your mind would like to change people and make them different.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.07,0:55:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The next big thing to have peace of mind
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.07,0:55:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is to let go wanting to get even.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.71,0:55:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that in the political arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.78,0:56:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Things the previous administration did, the new administration has to get into a make wrong and a get even
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.80,0:56:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because they want to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.71,0:56:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you can never see peace in the political arena
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.71,0:56:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're all up to proving others wrong, proving they're right,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.71,0:56:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying to get even with what the previous administration did 18 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.71,0:56:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to let go wanting to get even.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.05,0:56:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let go wanting to get even if you understand divine justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.53,0:56:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand divine justice, it saves you the bother of getting even
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.98,0:56:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because everything is taken care of by the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.42,0:56:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All things, then, karmically,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.42,0:56:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,have their own karmic payoff,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.42,0:56:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.42,0:57:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not necessary to bring down your enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.59,0:57:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because they will bring themselves down by their own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.59,0:57:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By their own hand, they will do themselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.75,0:57:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you're not stuck with the karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.07,0:57:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the minute you get even or get even with them
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.07,0:57:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,or conquer them, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.07,0:57:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you now have the karma of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.32,0:57:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody falls over, it's better that they do it of their own accord
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.32,0:57:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,than you're putting a bullet in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.73,0:57:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impolite to shoot people
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.63,0:57:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,without even asking their permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.90,0:57:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you really want peace above all else,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.38,0:57:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind thinks and the spirit knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.73,0:57:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So the spirit knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.80,0:58:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of wanting to get even
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.80,0:58:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go of wanting to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.80,0:58:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is extremely difficult in the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.80,0:58:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In our society, getting even and being right
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.80,0:58:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is considered a de rigueur.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.11,0:58:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.11,0:58:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other thing that goes on is making other people wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.96,0:58:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're right, then other people must be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.07,0:58:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The struggle for moral superiority of being right is intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.92,0:58:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So we learn to practice discernment rather than judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.44,0:58:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment and judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.76,0:58:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment, then, is interested in finding out
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.76,0:58:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the essence of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.76,0:58:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment is the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.76,0:59:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgmentalism, then, is seeking the moral high ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.51,0:59:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So we go to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.55,0:59:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to make these things come about in your own life
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.55,0:59:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is to silence opinionation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.55,0:59:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not necessary to have an opinion about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.88,0:59:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's not necessary to have an opinion about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.42,0:59:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need an opinion about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.21,0:59:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of such and such?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.21,0:59:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well, I really don't have an opinion about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.38,0:59:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.34,0:59:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Got no opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.34,0:59:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wishy-washy idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.34,0:59:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of our new Supreme Court justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.65,0:59:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.36,1:00:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the way things are going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.36,1:00:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In our society, this is the way things are going,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.86,1:00:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and such a thing is likely to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.86,1:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the waves go this way, they're not likely to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.00,1:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can stand back from society
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.00,1:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of being bobbled around by the waves
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.00,1:00:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the waves.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.38,1:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So we learn to be modest with our opinions.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.88,1:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We learn to perfect diplomacy, gentility.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.88,1:00:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't know what the upper classes are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.36,1:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They think the upper classes are having jets and big estates
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.36,1:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and lots of money.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.42,1:00:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't really know what the upper classes are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.42,1:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The upper classes, everybody's got money.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.42,1:00:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.51,1:00:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's got a title.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.51,1:00:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.25,1:00:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing was the capacity for diplomacy,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.69,1:01:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for diplomacy, graciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.98,1:01:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was once put up for one of the greatest,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.98,1:01:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,probably the most exclusive club in America.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.98,1:01:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a name I cannot even mention.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.98,1:01:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to meet all the really high people in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.98,1:01:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the New York City area,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.75,1:01:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the president of this, the president of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.75,1:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I told you all the titles, you'd say,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.75,1:01:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,did you expect them?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.75,1:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.32,1:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one quality that they had 100%.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.32,1:01:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the top, top people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.32,1:01:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Top, top.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.82,1:01:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The top of the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.01,1:01:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one of them was gracious.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.34,1:01:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one of them was gracious.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.34,1:01:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To be one of the top people in the world then,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.19,1:01:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing to do is to be gracious.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.40,1:01:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That means considerate of others,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.40,1:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,a sensitivity to others,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.51,1:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that they've been standing a long time,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.51,1:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you like a chair to sit?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.51,1:02:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been a long time without water,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.75,1:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,could I get you something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.75,1:02:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to put in another hour or two,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.92,1:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you say, how about a cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.92,1:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The one thing about the top people in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.28,1:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it was just stunning,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.28,1:02:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,was extremely gracious.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.34,1:02:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely gracious.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.05,1:02:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I met the richest, most powerful people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.53,1:02:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I come into their office and then say,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.53,1:02:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this is Dave Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.53,1:02:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who I want you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.53,1:02:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And he'd say,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.53,1:02:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,can I get you a cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.53,1:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit over here where the sun won't shine in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.11,1:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the big poobah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.40,1:02:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Make George Soros look like poor.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.00,1:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're solicitous of your comfort.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.48,1:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be solicitous then of the comfort of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.53,1:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This means not just physical comfort,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.53,1:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but their psychological comfort,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.53,1:03:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,their spiritual comfort.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.53,1:03:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody disagrees with me,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.53,1:03:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell them,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.53,1:03:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.53,1:03:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.53,1:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Disagreeing with me is fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.53,1:03:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.57,1:03:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want the person to be honest with who they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.57,1:03:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want them buttering me up with false yes men.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.57,1:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be modest with one's opinions.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.17,1:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll say,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.17,1:03:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems to me at this time
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.17,1:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is the way it appears to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.17,1:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that's flexible.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.17,1:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.23,1:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves room for you to move out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.23,1:03:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become diplomatic and genteel.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.48,1:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You become gracious and considerate of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.84,1:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,People say,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.96,1:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what's all this got to do with God?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.80,1:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God is gracious and considerate.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.28,1:04:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get to heaven,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.71,1:04:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.71,1:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,would you like to float on this cloud here?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.76,1:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to float over the sea?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.92,1:04:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So God comes disguised.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.71,1:04:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,God is disguised.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.71,1:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to be spiritually advanced
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.07,1:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize the God in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.71,1:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The God in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.71,1:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person who says to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.23,1:04:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,can I get you a cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.32,1:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.32,1:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've been on a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.32,1:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's talking to you is not him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.36,1:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's talking to you is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.15,1:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.15,1:04:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's God.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.15,1:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's God.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.15,1:04:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's divinity speaking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.15,1:04:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.15,1:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because divinity is that quality of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.15,1:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a personhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.15,1:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no gender.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.15,1:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No age.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.15,1:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentility.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.96,1:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Consideration for others.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.96,1:05:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also called unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.92,1:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional lovingness is concerned for the welfare of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.46,1:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting them first.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.76,1:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That they have the most comfortable seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.76,1:05:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.23,1:05:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be gracious and considerate.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.65,1:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And keep inner serenity as a goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.65,1:05:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Inner serenity as a goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.26,1:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of winning the argument
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.71,1:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you can't sleep all night?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.71,1:05:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I told him off.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.07,1:05:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, did I ever tell him off.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.07,1:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.23,1:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you keep a sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.23,1:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My secret weapon is a sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.03,1:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is comical when you look at it a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.13,1:06:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at it from really high space, everything is comical.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.46,1:06:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are people struggling to achieve all these things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.46,1:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, be modest with your opinions.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.75,1:06:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect diplomats' diplomatic skills and gentility.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.75,1:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Be gracious and considerate.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.94,1:06:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep serenity as a goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.57,1:06:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.40,1:06:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Or to have no opinion at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.40,1:06:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.86,1:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I don't know, I just haven't thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.86,1:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.86,1:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, well, that's being wishy-washy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.01,1:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I love being wishy-washy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.59,1:06:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wishy-washy, wishy-woo.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.59,1:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about so-and-so being on the Supreme Court?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.00,1:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think that's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.00,1:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At least she ain't out of a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.00,1:07:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't collecting unemployment.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.46,1:07:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people can't come from where she comes from.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.46,1:07:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or unemployment.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.78,1:07:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She ain't on unemployment.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.78,1:07:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Working for a living.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.46,1:07:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing you can do when you're undecided is to calibrate the options and be flexible.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.90,1:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is from an old friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.32,1:07:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not necessary to have an opinion on everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.32,1:07:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An old friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.76,1:07:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That I came out west with.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.84,1:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's his quote.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.86,1:07:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it in one of the books.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.86,1:07:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Put his name there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.86,1:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give his name away now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.07,1:07:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not giving away his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.07,1:07:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.07,1:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to have an opinion on everything or on anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.13,1:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what do you think about so-and-so?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.13,1:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.13,1:08:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just haven't given it much thought yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.13,1:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think about it after dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.78,1:08:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think about it after dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.77,1:08:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a lot to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.51,1:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I better move along.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.72,1:08:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, these are all practical.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.72,1:08:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to live a peaceful life and be peaceful, one of the first rules is avoid peace demonstrations.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.72,1:08:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All peace demonstrations are violent.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.92,1:08:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They got dogs, water cannons, shock machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.03,1:08:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They got police all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.03,1:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.03,1:08:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually what goes on at a peace demonstration is thuggery.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.88,1:09:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can start a riot anywhere in less than 10 minutes for $50.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.43,1:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.19,1:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They know better.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.96,1:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The communists learned how to do that, perfected the art of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.35,1:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For $50, you can start a riot anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.35,1:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how in case you want to start a riot.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.35,1:09:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be a commie.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.14,1:09:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to start a riot.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.72,1:09:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to the nearest low-class bar.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.72,1:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I got $50 here, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.98,1:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what I want you to do, there's some badass guys out there that stole my car and my girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.98,1:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want you to give them a good poke in the nose and teach them a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.98,1:09:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Any takers?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.81,1:09:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,$10 apiece, I can get five guys to leave any bar anytime.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.94,1:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have two shots and a beer when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.94,1:10:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, SOB.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.94,1:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom, boom, boom, boom, boom.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.94,1:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know, there's a riot on the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.94,1:10:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the call.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.94,1:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Brrr, call the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.94,1:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can start a riot anywhere in five minutes flat.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.27,1:10:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The communists perfected the technique of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.27,1:10:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Spontaneous demonstrations.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.27,1:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All spontaneous demonstrations are staged.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.97,1:10:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't staged, why would they all be there?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.97,1:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would 50 people be on a street corner?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.82,1:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people is there standing in the average New York street corner?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.07,1:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One or two, five maybe?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.07,1:10:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not 50.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.07,1:10:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you get 50 people on a street corner?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.07,1:10:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it by organized.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.43,1:10:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Community organizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.64,1:11:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called bar room organizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.64,1:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearest bar room will get you demonstrators in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.64,1:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And demonstrators love demonstrating, so they'll pull in more demonstrators.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.64,1:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know, the knuckles are going and the police are coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.64,1:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful excitement.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.64,1:11:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's adrenaline goes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.64,1:11:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.64,1:11:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you want to be peaceful, avoid peace demonstrations because they are too violent.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.53,1:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got police dogs, water cannons.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.75,1:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, this is useful, and I'll leave you with this thought while we take a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.75,1:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.18,1:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you who pine to be beautiful and rich and all, remember that Socrates was short and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.18,1:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be short and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.72,1:12:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates was short and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.75,1:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't tall and handsome.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.80,1:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates became world famous for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.80,1:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He was neither tall nor handsome nor rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.96,1:12:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we'll convene again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.43,1:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.43,1:12:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How soon is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.42,1:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.68,1:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Have one for the road.
